
'''Anne G. Mungai''' (wavutse 1957) ni umuyobozi wa firime yo muri Kenya. Azwi cyane muri firime ndende, ''Saikati'' (1992)<ref>https://www.adelphi.edu/news/dr-anne-mungai-named-associate-provost-for-strategic-initiatives-and-graduate-studies-at-adelphi/</ref>.  Azwiho gucukumbura inkuru z'abakobwa b'Abanyafrika bakiri bato n'ingorane bahura nazo mu gihe bagenda muri Afurika nyuma y'ubukoloni.<ref>https://www.adelphi.edu/directory/anne-mungai/</ref> 

== Ubuzima ==
Anne Mungai yahawe impamyabumenyi mu kigo cya [[Kenya]] gishinzwe itumanaho rusange  akomereza aho<ref>https://www.degruyter.com/database/IABO/entry/iab19972021/html</ref><ref>https://www.waterstones.com/author/anne-m-mungai/693583</ref>. Niwe washinze-umuyobozi w'ikinamico y'abana ya Shagilia.<ref>https://www.africanwomenincinema.org/AFWC/Mungai.html</ref> Mu 1993, Mungai yafatanyije gushinga Abagore muri Sinema muri [[Kenya]], ifatanya n’abagore b’abanyafurika muri Filime na Video nka komite y’agateganyo y’igice cyayo cya Kenya. <ref>Beti Ellerson, [https://www.africanwomenincinema.org/AFWC/Mungai.html Interview with Anne Mungai], 1997.</ref>

== Umwuga w'ubuyobozi ==
Umwuga wo kuyobora Anne Mungai watangiye mu 1980 n’igice gito cya mbere yise ''Nkomani Clinic.''<ref>https://www.amazon.co.uk/Books-Anne-Mungai/s?rh=n%3A266239%2Cp_27%3AAnne+Mungai</ref>  Kuva icyo gihe, yayoboye filime nyinshi ngufi-ndende, ndetse na filime ye ya mbere ''Saïkati.'' Iyi filime, kimwe n’ibikorwa byinshi bya Mungai<ref>https://www.standardmedia.co.ke/thenairobian/author/anne-mungai</ref>, yibanda ku miterere y’umugore uba muri Afurika mu gihe gitandukanijwe n’imigenzo gakondo y’umuco nyafurika n’izanwa mu bihugu by’iburengerazuba mu gihe cy'abakoloni. <ref>https://www.mwakilishi.com/article/diaspora-news/2020-02-26/kenyan-born-anne-mungai-named-associate-provost</ref>

